### ===== LANDING PAGE ENDPOINTS =====

### Get all carousel items
GET http://gratex.net/api/landing/carousel
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get all services
GET http://gratex.net/api/landing/services
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Add a carousel item (with image upload)
POST http://gratex.net/api/landing/carousel
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Welcome to Gratex
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="subtitle"

Your trusted partner
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test-carousel.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------Boundary--

###

### Add a service (with image upload)
POST http://gratex.net/api/landing/services
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Web Development
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Professional web development services
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test-service.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------Boundary--

###

### Delete a carousel item (by ID in body)
DELETE http://gratex.net/api/landing/carousel
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1
}

###

### Delete a carousel item (by ID in query string)
DELETE http://gratex.net/api/landing/carousel?id=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Delete a service (by ID in body)
DELETE http://gratex.net/api/landing/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1
}

###

### Delete a service (by ID in query string)
DELETE http://gratex.net/api/landing/services?id=1
Content-Type: application/json
